name: Venom Skull
description: Lob an explosive skull at an enemy, dealing 2160 Poison Damage.  Every third cast of this ability deals 20% increased damage.  While slotted, casting any Necromancer ability while you are in combat will count towards the third cast.
effectLines: Converts into a Stamina ability and deals Poison Damage. Casting any Necromancer ability counts towards the third cast.
